rate accretion luminosities, the supply of\ncold gas primarily determines the accretion rate distribution of the nuclear\nblack holes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Feb 2013 21:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 May 2013 12:38:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
