tal adsorbates the direction\nof the charge transfer is from adsorbate to silicene, because of its high\nsurface reactivity. Our results indicate that the reactive crystal structure of\nsilicene provides a rich playground for functionalization at nanoscale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Feb 2013 12:03:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-22"}
