d to social position calculation was introduced along with\nresults of comparison between their processing time and others centrality\nmethods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Feb 2013 13:47:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2013 08:38:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-12"}
